	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingero</persName> suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. Cum subito comitia propter inexpectatum cęsaris mandatum solverentur,<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Kaiser <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Karl V.</persName> hatte am 15. Januar die Beendigung des <placeName ref="l569" cert="high">Wormser</placeName> Kolloquiums angeordnet; s. <bibl>ADRG</bibl> II/1 208-2 10, <ref target="file10142">Nr. 112</ref> (vgl. den Abschied vom 18. Januar, <bibl>ADRG</bibl> II/1 210f, <ref target="file10143">Nr. 113</ref>; <bibl>MO</bibl> IV 79).</note> scribere ad vos fratres, qualiter voluerunt, non potuerunt.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Philippus</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Philipp Melanchthon</persName>.</note> ipse mihi promisit ad te se scripturum<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>In er Vorlage</hi> scriptum.</note> diligenter esse<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Ein entsprechender Brief ist nicht nachweisbar.</note>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cęterorum unusquisque scribere paratus fuerat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque oro te, ut, quod non multorum literas adfero ad vos, velitis imputare necessitati.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> tota vos pie colit et diligit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1365" cert="high">S. Grynęus</persName> tuus.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">2. februarii.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
